title: MultiBeast - Mavericks 6.0.1
description:
MultiBeast 6.0 Update

MultiBeast, the ultimate post-installation utility, has been updated to version 6.0 for OS X Mavericks. It's been completely rewritten from the ground up as a native OS X application. As well as the many design changes, we've also included new 10.9 AppleHDA audio drivers, Haswell iMac smbioses, automatic serial number generation and special fixes relevant to OS 10.9 Mavericks.
